# GIT AI COMMIT

AI-powered commit message generator using Claude AI.

## Installation

```bash
npm install -g git-panda
```

## Setup
```bash
git-panda config set-key YOUR-API-KEY
```

## Usage
```bash
git .
git-panda
```

## Command
### Show config
```bash
git-panda config show
```

## Features

- Smart commit message generation with Claude AI
- Follow Conventional Commits standard
- Cost-effective (~$0.0015 per commit)
- Fast and interactive
- Beautiful CLI interface

